reviewText: No, I wasn't satisfied, it doesn't even work, can't watch it,
It is a very interesting movie about my favorite Beckham

This is a really interesting look at the years that David Beckham has spent at Man U. The one thing that got a little repetitive was the fact that they showed allll of his goals. If they had more interviews and just some overviews I would have given it 5 stars. Even though some parts are long its a great look at David Beckham's career!!!....So ENJOY IT!!

this is a great video that highlights becks moments at united...but its also sad as a man utd supporter since birth its very hard video i would rather not say bye to becks but hey things happend ..its a must have for any becks supporter and man utd supporter that likes to remember old times.
